column10:
DayZ without Zombies,
Tarkov without extraction;
This is the best game I've played recently

I like the idea of AI ( bandits ) , missions,etc but the map is pretty much, empty, the few big buildings that you encounter you cant even enter them, how difficult can be to put a few more buildings with some loot inside? , and why in a survival game you cant drink from ponds, rivers an such?

//

Now that the last patch is live, the game crashes with a fatal error at the start.

//
A year later and the game is still the same, a survival game with no animals to hunt and eat and a walking simulator because they are incapable of putting one single , simple, working , vehicle. I wont be coming back anytime soon.
